column1: Daily Weather Observations for Walpole, Western Australia for July 2024
Prepared at 13:03 UTC on Monday  4 November 2024   IDCJDW6138.202407

The North Walpole observation site is approximately 3 kilometres north-northwest of Walpole and at higher elevation, so significantly different conditions may be experienced at the two places on particular days.
Observations were drawn from North Walpole {station 009998}
